&lt;h1 id="life-is-lived-in-the-arena"&gt;Life is Lived in The Arena&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jul 17 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
Life is lived in the arena. You only learn by doing. And if you&amp;rsquo;re not doing, then all the learning you&amp;rsquo;re picking up is too general and too abstract. Then it truly is Hallmark aphorisms. You don&amp;rsquo;t know what applies where and when.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>